{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":920,"text":"What started as a platform for hobbyists"},{"time":2920,"text":"is poised to become\na multibillion-dollar industry."},{"time":5880,"text":"Inspection, environmental monitoring,\nphotography and film and journalism:"},{"time":9960,"text":"these are some of the potential\napplications for commercial drones,"},{"time":13160,"text":"and their enablers\nare the capabilities being developed"},{"time":15800,"text":"at research facilities around the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":17760,"text":"For example, before aerial\npackage delivery"},{"time":20400,"text":"entered our social consciousness,"},{"time":22240,"text":"an autonomous fleet of flying machines\nbuilt a six-meter-tall tower"},{"time":26240,"text":"composed of 1,500 bricks"},{"time":28200,"text":"in front of a live audience\nat the FRAC Centre in France,"},{"time":31160,"text":"and several years ago,\nthey started to fly with ropes."},{"time":33760,"text":"By tethering flying machines,"},{"time":35200,"text":"they can achieve high speeds\nand accelerations in very tight spaces."},{"time":39000,"text":"They can also autonomously build\ntensile structures."},{"time":42120,"text":"Skills learned include how to carry loads,"},{"time":44560,"text":"how to cope with disturbances,"},{"time":46040,"text":"and in general, how to interact\nwith the physical world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49160,"text":"Today we want to show you some\nnew projects that we've been working on."},{"time":52520,"text":"Their aim is to push the boundary\nof what can be achieved"},{"time":55480,"text":"with autonomous flight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57040,"text":"Now, for a system to function\nautonomously,"},{"time":59520,"text":"it must collectively know the location\nof its mobile objects in space."},{"time":64000,"text":"Back at our lab at ETH Zurich,"},{"time":65920,"text":"we often use external cameras\nto locate objects,"},{"time":68800,"text":"which then allows us to focus our efforts"},{"time":70800,"text":"on the rapid development\nof highly dynamic tasks."},{"time":73480,"text":"For the demos you will see today, however,"},{"time":75560,"text":"we will use new localization technology\ndeveloped by Verity Studios,"},{"time":78880,"text":"a spin-off from our lab."},{"time":80520,"text":"There are no external cameras."},{"time":82160,"text":"Each flying machine uses onboard sensors\nto determine its location in space"},{"time":87240,"text":"and onboard computation\nto determine what its actions should be."},{"time":91280,"text":"The only external commands\nare high-level ones"},{"time":93480,"text":"such as \"take off\" and \"land.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":118560,"text":"This is a so-called tail-sitter."},{"time":120480,"text":"It's an aircraft that tries\nto have its cake and eat it."},{"time":123960,"text":"Like other fixed-wing aircraft,\nit is efficient in forward flight,"},{"time":127240,"text":"much more so than helicopters\nand variations thereof."},{"time":130479,"text":"Unlike most other\nfixed-wing aircraft, however,"},{"time":132920,"text":"it is capable of hovering,"},{"time":134440,"text":"which has huge advantages\nfor takeoff, landing"},{"time":137600,"text":"and general versatility."},{"time":139480,"text":"There is no free lunch, unfortunately."},{"time":141600,"text":"One of the limitations with tail-sitters"},{"time":143560,"text":"is that they're susceptible\nto disturbances such as wind gusts."},{"time":146560,"text":"We're developing new control\narchitectures and algorithms"},{"time":149280,"text":"that address this limitation."},{"time":158560,"text":"The idea is for the aircraft to recover"},{"time":160840,"text":"no matter what state it finds itself in,"},{"time":171400,"text":"and through practice,\nimprove its performance over time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183600,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":190000,"text":"OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201480,"text":"When doing research,"},{"time":202720,"text":"we often ask ourselves\nfundamental abstract questions"},{"time":205720,"text":"that try to get at the heart of a matter."},{"time":209240,"text":"For example, one such question would be,"},{"time":211480,"text":"what is the minimum number of moving parts\nneeded for controlled flight?"},{"time":215520,"text":"Now, there are practical reasons"},{"time":217120,"text":"why you may want to know\nthe answer to such a question."},{"time":219760,"text":"Helicopters, for example,"},{"time":221040,"text":"are affectionately known\nas machines with a thousand moving parts"},{"time":224920,"text":"all conspiring to do you bodily harm."},{"time":228640,"text":"It turns out that decades ago,"},{"time":230520,"text":"skilled pilots were able to fly\nremote-controlled aircraft"},{"time":233720,"text":"that had only two moving parts:"},{"time":235640,"text":"a propeller and a tail rudder."},{"time":238000,"text":"We recently discovered\nthat it could be done with just one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241600,"text":"This is the monospinner,"},{"time":242880,"text":"the world's mechanically simplest\ncontrollable flying machine,"},{"time":246160,"text":"invented just a few months ago."},{"time":247960,"text":"It has only one moving part, a propeller."},{"time":251120,"text":"It has no flaps, no hinges, no ailerons,"},{"time":254720,"text":"no other actuators,\nno other control surfaces,"},{"time":257279,"text":"just a simple propeller."},{"time":259320,"text":"Even though it's mechanically simple,"},{"time":261399,"text":"there's a lot going on\nin its little electronic brain"},{"time":263920,"text":"to allow it to fly in a stable fashion\nand to move anywhere it wants in space."},{"time":268160,"text":"Even so, it doesn't yet have"},{"time":269640,"text":"the sophisticated algorithms\nof the tail-sitter,"},{"time":272000,"text":"which means that in order\nto get it to fly,"},{"time":274024,"text":"I have to throw it just right."},{"time":276800,"text":"And because the probability\nof me throwing it just right is very low,"},{"time":280840,"text":"given everybody watching me,"},{"time":282760,"text":"what we're going to do instead"},{"time":284240,"text":"is show you a video\nthat we shot last night."}]},{"cues":[{"time":286440,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":298320,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":311080,"text":"If the monospinner\nis an exercise in frugality,"},{"time":314840,"text":"this machine here, the omnicopter,\nwith its eight propellers,"},{"time":318320,"text":"is an exercise in excess."},{"time":320920,"text":"What can you do with all this surplus?"},{"time":323080,"text":"The thing to notice\nis that it is highly symmetric."},{"time":325920,"text":"As a result, it is ambivalent\nto orientation."},{"time":328800,"text":"This gives it an extraordinary capability."},{"time":331520,"text":"It can move anywhere it wants in space"},{"time":333760,"text":"irrespective of where it is facing"},{"time":336520,"text":"and even of how it is rotating."},{"time":339040,"text":"It has its own complexities,"},{"time":340440,"text":"mainly having to do\nwith the interacting flows"},{"time":343120,"text":"from its eight propellers."},{"time":344680,"text":"Some of this can be modeled,\nwhile the rest can be learned on the fly."},{"time":348560,"text":"Let's take a look."}]},{"cues":[{"time":392760,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":400720,"text":"If flying machines are going\nto enter part of our daily lives,"},{"time":403649,"text":"they will need to become\nextremely safe and reliable."},{"time":406760,"text":"This machine over here"},{"time":408160,"text":"is actually two separate\ntwo-propeller flying machines."},{"time":411320,"text":"This one wants to spin clockwise."},{"time":413080,"text":"This other one wants\nto spin counterclockwise."},{"time":415600,"text":"When you put them together,"},{"time":416960,"text":"they behave like one\nhigh-performance quadrocopter."},{"time":431640,"text":"If anything goes wrong, however --"},{"time":433320,"text":"a motor fails, a propeller fails,\nelectronics, even a battery pack --"},{"time":437800,"text":"the machine can still fly,\nalbeit in a degraded fashion."},{"time":441160,"text":"We're going to demonstrate this to you now\nby disabling one of its halves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464240,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":471320,"text":"This last demonstration"},{"time":472680,"text":"is an exploration of synthetic swarms."},{"time":475560,"text":"The large number of autonomous,\ncoordinated entities"},{"time":478560,"text":"offers a new palette\nfor aesthetic expression."},{"time":481320,"text":"We've taken commercially available\nmicro quadcopters,"},{"time":484320,"text":"each weighing less\nthan a slice of bread, by the way,"},{"time":486840,"text":"and outfitted them\nwith our localization technology"},{"time":489280,"text":"and custom algorithms."},{"time":490880,"text":"Because each unit\nknows where it is in space"},{"time":493000,"text":"and is self-controlled,"},{"time":494400,"text":"there is really no limit to their number."}]},{"cues":[{"time":523840,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":547360,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":606040,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":623960,"text":"Hopefully, these demonstrations\nwill motivate you to dream up"},{"time":627080,"text":"new revolutionary roles\nfor flying machines."},{"time":630560,"text":"That ultrasafe one over there for example"},{"time":632680,"text":"has aspirations to become\na flying lampshade on Broadway."}]},{"cues":[{"time":635720,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":637800,"text":"The reality is that it is\ndifficult to predict"},{"time":640000,"text":"the impact of nascent technology."},{"time":642120,"text":"And for folks like us, the real reward\nis the journey and the act of creation."},{"time":647000,"text":"It's a continual reminder"},{"time":648440,"text":"of how wonderful and magical\nthe universe we live in is,"},{"time":651840,"text":"that it allows creative, clever creatures"},{"time":654800,"text":"to sculpt it in such spectacular ways."},{"time":657800,"text":"The fact that this technology"},{"time":659600,"text":"has such huge commercial\nand economic potential"},{"time":663040,"text":"is just icing on the cake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":664480,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":665720,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}